iterations.yara_rule:
rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 53 FF 15 ?? ?? ?? ?? 33 FF }  // ExitProcess call with surrounding context
        $pattern1 = { 50 FF 15 ?? ?? ?? ?? 33 FF }  // CloseHandle call with surrounding context
        $pattern2 = { E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? A1 ?? ?? ?? ?? }  // Debugger check call with memory access

    condition:
        any of them
}
iterations.failure_reason: Rule hit but no new signatures
improvement_suggestions: Replace FF 15 with E8 in $pattern0 and $pattern1 to match relative calls. Adjust skip offsets to avoid invalid jumps.
